# Environment Variables Setup Guide

## Root-level (.env.local or Vercel Environment Variables)

```
# Supabase
SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxx.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your_service_key_here

# JWT Secret (generate a strong random string)
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_change_this

# Qwen AI (Alibaba DashScope API) - OpenAI Compatible Mode ✅ RECOMMENDED
# 使用 OpenAI SDK 通过兼容模式调用千问 API（最简洁方案）
DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=sk-xxxxx  # Get from https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/user
# 备选方式（如需直接调用）
QWEN_API_KEY=sk-xxxxx

# Stripe
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_xxxxx
STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_live_xxxxx
STRIPE_BASIC_PRICE_ID=price_xxxxx_basic
STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=price_xxxxx_pro

# Application URLs
VERCEL_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app
```

## Frontend Environment (.env or .env.local in 每日科技脉搏 app/)

```
# Public Stripe Key (can be exposed)
REACT_APP_STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_live_xxxxx

# API Base URL
REACT_APP_API_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app
```

## How to Get These Values

### Qwen AI Setup (通义千问)
1. Visit https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com
2. Sign up with Alibaba Cloud account or create new account
3. Go to API Keys section
4. Create a new API key
5. Copy the key and set as QWEN_API_KEY or DASHSCOPE_API_KEY

### Supabase Setup
1. Visit https://supabase.com
2. Create a new project
3. Go to Project Settings → API
4. Copy "Project URL" and "anon public key"
5. Copy "service_role key" from the same page

### Stripe Setup
1. Visit https://stripe.com
2. Create account and verify
3. Go to Developers → API Keys
4. Copy "Secret Key"
5. Create products for each plan
6. Copy Price IDs from product settings

### JWT Secret
Generate using:
```bash
node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
```

## Vercel Deployment

1. Go to your Vercel project settings
2. Click "Environment Variables"
3. Add all the variables above
4. Redeploy your project
